# üêû bug report

### Affected Package
None


### Is this a regression?

No


### Description

When I deploy in production my Angular app, I can install it as a PWA without any problem, with Chrome. But in my code, I have to open in several case another window, but it always opens in a new Chrome tab instead of new PWA window, despite many configurations...
Here is what i tried :
- change the target in the window.open
- use router with createUrlTree
- use [routerLink] in html for navigation with target attribute
- configure scope and start_url properly in manifest.webmanifest (start_url: ./ and scope: .)


